132
00:06:29,845 --> 00:06:30,285
Come on.

133
00:06:32,645 --> 00:06:33,244
Jin.

134
00:06:34,324 --> 00:06:35,564
Stay.

135
00:06:37,244 --> 00:06:39,244
While the two of you are here,

136
00:06:39,965 --> 00:06:42,045
