137
00:06:45,085 --> 00:06:45,965
Over the years,

138
00:06:46,684 --> 00:06:47,765
there is so much

139
00:06:47,884 --> 00:06:49,244
I want to tell you.

140
00:06:51,285 --> 00:06:52,484
