142
00:06:56,684 --> 00:06:57,765
while we're here.

143
00:07:00,165 --> 00:07:00,645
I know

144
00:07:02,244 --> 00:07:05,924
I made you suffer a lot in the past.

145
00:07:07,324 --> 00:07:08,645
You had to endure a lot.

146
00:07:10,244 --> 00:07:13,965
I left a lot of regrets in your life.

147
00:07:15,324 --> 00:07:16,444
I kept trying to stay by your side

148
00:07:17,205 --> 00:07:19,124
all these years

149
00:07:20,004 --> 00:07:23,564
because I wanted to make up for those things.

150
00:07:27,205 --> 00:07:27,684
I know

151
00:07:27,804 --> 00:07:30,124
our first marriage was a failure.

152
00:07:31,405 --> 00:07:32,605
So I was wondering

153
00:07:34,804 --> 00:07:37,845
if you could give me a chance

154
00:07:39,605 --> 00:07:42,605
and let me stay with you

155
00:07:43,165 --> 00:07:48,285
and take care of you.

156
00:07:56,564 --> 00:07:58,085
Ms. Lin… No.

157
00:07:59,564 --> 00:08:00,444
Lin.

158
00:08:08,364 --> 00:08:11,725
Will you marry me again?

159
00:08:21,684 --> 00:08:23,804
I've been waiting
to hear that all this time.

160
00:08:25,525 --> 00:08:26,244
I think

161
00:08:27,484 --> 00:08:30,045
