181
00:09:57,444 --> 00:09:59,084
The woman he loved for ten years

182
00:09:59,245 --> 00:10:00,204
is marrying someone else.

183
00:10:00,405 --> 00:10:01,444
He doesn't stand a chance anymore.

184
00:10:01,844 --> 00:10:02,724
Nonsense.

185
00:10:03,125 --> 00:10:04,084
We've already closed that chapter.

186
00:10:04,684 --> 00:10:05,485
Just kidding.

187
00:10:05,765 --> 00:10:07,125
Huo is probably annoyed

188
00:10:07,245 --> 00:10:08,765
about Yu Shishi ignoring him.

189
00:10:11,844 --> 00:10:13,564
Well, you have to invite Huo

190
00:10:13,964 --> 00:10:15,005
