210
00:10:55,084 --> 00:10:56,204
I'll treat her well.

211
00:10:56,804 --> 00:10:58,604
Don't forget to show up on time.

212
00:10:59,765 --> 00:11:00,924
I will.

213
00:11:02,045 --> 00:11:02,485
Thanks.

214
00:11:03,525 --> 00:11:04,084
By the way,

215
00:11:05,765 --> 00:11:07,885
I need a favour.

216
00:11:09,724 --> 00:11:10,724
Invite someone for me.

217
00:11:31,885 --> 00:11:32,245
Doesn't it look nice,

218
00:11:32,804 --> 00:11:33,444
Mom?

219
00:11:35,324 --> 00:11:36,245
When my father saw you

220
00:11:36,324 --> 00:11:37,444
in that wedding dress,

221
00:11:37,885 --> 00:11:39,204
there were sparkles in his eyes.

222
00:11:43,005 --> 00:11:44,045
You have a way with words,

223
00:11:44,645 --> 00:11:45,604
just like your father.

224
00:11:51,005 --> 00:11:51,564
Mom,

225
00:11:52,324 --> 00:11:54,084
I made you and Dad worry about me

226
00:11:54,084 --> 00:11:54,924
all these years.

227
00:11:57,885 --> 00:11:58,964
But you don't have

228
00:11:59,444 --> 00:12:00,444
to worry about me anymore.

229
00:12:01,324 --> 00:12:04,684
Jin Shichuan will look after me.

230
00:12:06,645 --> 00:12:08,285
You and Dad should just

231
00:12:09,525 --> 00:12:10,765
enjoy your life together.

232
00:12:16,964 --> 00:12:17,765
Actually,

233
00:12:18,084 --> 00:12:19,645
I owe you an apology.

234
00:12:21,204 --> 00:12:22,045
When you were young,

235
00:12:22,204 --> 00:12:23,045
we made you

236
00:12:23,125 --> 00:12:24,245
see your parents fighting too often.

237
00:12:25,084 --> 00:12:26,204
You had to endure a lot of grievances.

238
00:12:27,525 --> 00:12:28,684
Looking back on it now,

239
00:12:30,045 --> 00:12:31,485
we owe you so much.

240
00:12:34,405 --> 00:12:35,645
I'm sorry, my dear.

241
00:12:36,285 --> 00:12:37,165
It's okay.

242
00:12:39,285 --> 00:12:41,245
We were young back then.

243
00:12:41,924 --> 00:12:42,924
We didn't know
how to maintain a marriage.

244
00:12:43,285 --> 00:12:44,724
It was our first time being parents.

245
00:12:45,924 --> 00:12:47,444
We had to learn and figure out

246
00:12:48,084 --> 00:12:49,684
how to get along through the years too.

247
00:12:51,765 --> 00:12:52,564
I wondered

248
00:12:52,645 --> 00:12:54,964
why I kept arguing
with your father back then.

249
00:12:55,804 --> 00:12:56,604
Then, I realized

250
00:12:58,045 --> 00:13:00,485
that it was because I wanted to see him

251
00:13:01,045 --> 00:13:02,045
but I couldn't.

252
00:13:04,444 --> 00:13:05,724
Maybe that's what love is.

253
00:13:09,765 --> 00:13:10,604
Before this,

254
00:13:12,204 --> 00:13:13,765
I always wanted you

255
00:13:15,045 --> 00:13:18,005
to marry an ordinary man

256
00:13:18,564 --> 00:13:20,005
and live a peaceful life.

257
00:13:20,405 --> 00:13:21,645
But I've seen your love

258
00:13:21,684 --> 00:13:23,084
with my own eyes.

259
00:13:27,844 --> 00:13:29,885
It's not easy
to be the wife of a firefighter.

260
00:13:32,365 --> 00:13:33,604
But it is your decision,

261
00:13:33,724 --> 00:13:35,245
and I will respect that and support you.

262
00:13:38,645 --> 00:13:41,885
I hope my daughter will be happy.

263
00:13:48,804 --> 00:13:49,444
Mom.

264
00:13:52,444 --> 00:13:53,924
We will be happy.

265
00:13:54,324 --> 00:13:54,844
We will.

266
00:13:55,765 --> 00:13:57,045
We will be happy.

267
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:28,700
(Xu Lai  Jin Shichuan)

268
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:42,140
(Xu Lai  Jin Shichuan)

269
00:14:46,005 --> 00:14:46,645
Captain Jin,

270
00:14:46,885 --> 00:14:47,924
