271
00:14:49,564 --> 00:14:50,245
No.

272
00:14:51,045 --> 00:14:52,285
How can he not be?
It's his first time getting married.

273
00:14:53,405 --> 00:14:54,604
Where's Xu Lai? Is she here yet?

274
00:14:54,964 --> 00:14:55,405
No.

275
00:14:57,084 --> 00:14:58,005
Congratulations, Captain Jin.

276
00:14:58,045 --> 00:14:58,405
Thank you.

277
00:14:58,485 --> 00:14:59,045
