278
00:14:59,285 --> 00:15:00,084
Thank you.

279
00:15:00,804 --> 00:15:01,285
Congratulations, Captain Jin.

280
00:15:01,285 --> 00:15:01,724
Thank you.

281
00:15:09,204 --> 00:15:10,045
We've watched

282
00:15:10,125 --> 00:15:11,724
Captain Jin and Xu Lai come a long way.

283
00:15:11,924 --> 00:15:12,964
I suppose this is a happy ending.

284
00:15:14,245 --> 00:15:14,804
They are two lovers

285
00:15:14,924 --> 00:15:16,444
