of the universe.)

620
00:36:14,965 --> 00:36:16,325
(And you've been by my side)

621
00:36:17,724 --> 00:36:19,005
(like Charon.)

622
00:36:20,564 --> 00:36:21,845
(Thank you for being with me)

623
00:36:22,365 --> 00:36:23,325
(on my loneliest)

624
00:36:23,325 --> 00:36:24,244
(journey.)

625
00:36:25,885 --> 00:36:26,564
(I hope)

626
00:36:27,604 --> 00:36:29,124
(that you will soon find the meaning)

627
00:36:29,124 --> 00:36:30,005
(you are searching for in your life.)

628
00:36:37,066 --> 00:36:39,966
