than a romance.

658
00:38:06,764 --> 00:38:07,885
(Xu Lai has been)

659
00:38:08,164 --> 00:38:08,764
(through countless dangers)

660
00:38:08,805 --> 00:38:09,805
(with Captain Jin.)

661
00:38:11,005 --> 00:38:12,204
