00:38:38,644 --> 00:38:39,845
Are you alone, Miss?

665
00:38:40,525 --> 00:38:41,965
Yes. What about it?

666
00:38:43,805 --> 00:38:46,005
What a coincidence. I'm alone too.

667
00:38:47,805 --> 00:38:50,284
Want to date me?

668
00:38:51,925 --> 00:38:53,045
I'm very demanding

669
