670
00:38:54,684 --> 00:38:57,485
I don't date guys who aren't my type.

671
00:38:58,084 --> 00:39:01,045
So tell me what your type is.

672
00:39:05,644 --> 00:39:08,604
I like someone with bushy eyebrows,

673
00:39:09,805 --> 00:39:11,005
a high nose,

674
00:39:11,885 --> 00:39:13,805
bright puppy-like eyes,

675
00:39:14,244 --> 00:39:16,885
who knows everything about me

676
00:39:17,124 --> 00:39:18,764
and never gives up,

677
00:39:19,405 --> 00:39:20,405
and tells me

678
00:39:20,604 --> 00:39:21,885
lots of stories

679
00:39:22,244 --> 00:39:23,204
to make me happy.

680
00:39:26,684 --> 00:39:28,124
I happen to know someone

681
00:39:28,204 --> 00:39:28,925
like that.

682
00:39:31,164 --> 00:39:32,644
Care to meet him in person?

683
00:39:33,204 --> 00:39:33,684
Sure.

684
00:39:35,365 --> 00:39:36,805
But I want to test the goods first.

685
00:39:48,925 --> 00:39:49,644
Satisfied?

686
00:39:52,405 --> 00:39:53,805
How long is my probation?

687
00:39:55,965 --> 00:39:56,925
For life.

688
