694
00:40:50,485 --> 00:40:51,724
and seen a lot of sights.

695
00:40:52,485 --> 00:40:54,084
Then I realized

696
00:40:54,564 --> 00:40:55,124
that this was still

697
00:40:55,204 --> 00:40:56,284
the place I wanted to be.

698
00:41:05,244 --> 00:41:05,805
Let's go.

699
00:41:14,764 --> 00:41:15,564
You have the day off tomorrow.

700
00:41:16,005 --> 00:41:16,724
Let's go out.

701
00:41:20,164 --> 00:41:21,684
I'll go wherever you want to go.

702
00:41:22,644 --> 00:41:23,325
Really?

703
00:41:27,885 --> 00:41:29,005
Not bad, Hubby.

704
00:41:29,204 --> 00:41:29,885
That's your reward.

705
00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:32,380
♪When the sky hesitates to blue♪

